						               													<description>In the multiplayer roll and write game Aban!, your goal is to completely plant your garden and score the highest number. In each round, you roll dice in the center of the table, determining what plants are available to all players. You have to draw these paths on your player sheets to create combos between plants and sabotage the garden of the other players. You will be trying to optimize the available symbols better than your opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Aban! Comes with double-sided cards and different effects that add new unique strategies to your games. In addition, the different cards and variability in the dice can be animated and make every game different. Aban! Allows you to play from 2 to 5 players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
